  "body": "### Description\nAs a user, I do not want my sync to stall so that I can get up and running as fast as possible. In a post-Merge environment, there are some changes to sync that may help with this, like\n- PoS Friendly sync target\n- Peer shuffling to avoid trying to peer with the same node over and over \n- Re-Evaluating best-peer rules in post-Merge context\n- Better logging in a stuck sync  \n\n### Acceptance Criteria\n- Clearer or better sync process \n\n**NEED TIMING / SCOPE ESTIMATE FOR THIS** \n\n### Steps to Reproduce (Bug)\n1. Have a sync stall\n\n**Expected behavior:** [What you expect to happen]\n- Completed sync \n\n**Actual behavior:** [What actually happens]\n\n**Frequency:** [What percentage of the time does it occur?]\n\n### Versions (Add all that apply)\n* Software version: latest",
